     ******************************************************************
     **  プログラム名   : PILOT KANBAN OUTPUT                      **
     **                   : （新規発行）　　　　　　　　　　　     **
     **  プログラムＩＤ :  MRHR42     <RPG>                        **
     **  作成年月日     :  2014/02/06                              **
     **  作成者         :  TR-ITS                                  **
     **  プログラム概要 : 試作かんばんの発行用データを出力する   **
     **                   : （新規発行）　　　　　　　　　　　     **
     **--------------------------------------------------------------**
     **  変更年月日     :  YYYY/MM/DD                              **
     **  変更者         :                                          **
     **  変更内容       :                                          **
     ******************************************************************
     ** <<使用標識説明>>
     **        80       :試作手配データファイル読込
     **        81       :その他マスタ読込
     ******************************************************************
     H            Y/                                    1
     **==============================================================**
     **  ファイル
     **==============================================================**
     F*<<試作手配データファイル(L3)>>
     FMRHPL53 UF  E           K        DISK
     F*<<細目コード管理マスタ>>
     FFGBPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     F*<<試作かんばん発行データファイル>>
     FMRHPP61 O   E                    DISK
     **==============================================================**
     **  配列
     **==============================================================**
      *
     **==============================================================**
     **  ＤＳ
     **==============================================================**
     I*<<システム情報>>
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM S@PGID
     I                                      244 253 S@WSID
     I                                      254 263 S@USID
     I                                      264 269 S@JBID
     I*<<システム日時>>
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140S@TIME
     I                                        1   60S@HMS
     I                                        1   20S@TMHH
     I                                        3   40S@TMMM
     I                                        5   60S@TMSS
     I                                        7  140S@YYMD
     I                                        7  100S@DYYY
     I                                       11  120S@DYMM
     I                                       13  140S@DYDD
     **--------------------------------------------------------------**
     I* <<ファイル・削除年月日>>
      *細目コード管理マスタ(FGBPL01)
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80B2SKHZ
     I                                        1   40B2SKYY
     I                                        5   60B2SKMM
     I                                        7   80B2SKDD
     I* <<バーコード項目>>
      * SURFACE TREATMENT BARCODE
     I            DS
     I                                        1  15 SKMKBA
     I                                        1   1 SKMKB1
     I                                        2   8 SKMKB2
     I                                        9  10 SKMKB3
     I                                       11  14 SKMKB4
     I                                       15  15 SKMKCD
     I                                        1  14 SKMKB
      * CHECK GATE BARCODE
     I            DS
     I                                        1   7 SKCGBA
     I                                        1   4 SKCGB1
     I                                        5   7 SKCGB2
      * OQ BARCODE
     I            DS
     I                                        1  11 SKOQBA
     I                                        1   3 SKOQB1
     I                                        4   6 SKOQB2
     I                                        7  10 SKOQB3
     I                                       11  11 SKOQCD
     I                                        1  10 SKOQB
      * LOQ BARCODE
     I            DS
     I                                        1   7 SKLOQB
     I                                        1   3 SKLOQ1
     I                                        4   6 SKLOQ2
     I                                        7   7 SKLOQC
     I                                        1   6 SKLOQ
      *
     **==============================================================**
     **  パラメータ
     **==============================================================**
      *
     **==============================================================**
     **  ＫＥＹ
     **==============================================================**
     C* <<試作手配データファイル(MRHPL53)>>
     C           STKEY     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           W@HKHZ           *かんばん発行日
     C* <<細目コード管理マスタ(FGBPL01) >>
     C           B2KEY     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           B2CODE           *細目コード
      *
     **==============================================================**
     **  メインルーチン
     **==============================================================**
      *
      *---<初期処理>---*
     C                     EXSR #INIT
      *
     C                     EXSR #RED10
      *---<主処理>---*
     C           *IN80     DOWEQ'0'                        ¬DO_01
     C                     EXSR #DBOUT
     C                     EXSR #RED10
     C                     END                             ｢DO_01
      *
      *---<終了処理>---*
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
      **************************************************************************
      *         Ｓ　Ｕ　Ｂ　－　Ｒ　Ｏ　Ｕ　Ｔ　Ｉ　Ｎ　Ｅ
      **************************************************************************
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      *          #INIT    初期処理
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #INIT     BEGSR
      *
     C                     TIME           S@TIME
      *
      *試作手配データファイル(MRHPL53)
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     W@HKHZ  80       *かんばん発行日
     C           STKEY     SETLLMRHPL531
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      *          #RED10   試作手配データファイル　読込
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #RED10    BEGSR
      *
     C                     DO   *HIVAL                     ¬DO_01
     C           STKEY     READEMRHPL531                 80
      *
     C   80                LEAVE
      *<対象範囲データ抽出>
      *削除データ
     C           STGSJY    IFEQ 'D'                        ~¬IF_01
     C           STGSHZ    ANDLES@YYMD
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF                           _｢IF_01
      *
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDDO                           ｢DO_01
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      *          #DBOUT   出力処理
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #DBOUT    BEGSR
      *試作かんばんデータファイル(MRHPP61)出力
     C                     CLEARMRHPP611
     C                     EXSR #MOV10
     C                     WRITEMRHPP611
      *
      *試作手配データファイル(MRHPL53)更新
     C                     EXSR #MOV20
     C                     UPDATMRHPL531
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      *          #MOV10   項目移送処理
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #MOV10    BEGSR
      *試作かんばんデータファイル(MRHPP61)
     C                     MOVELSTTHI1    SKTHI1           *LOT NUMBER 1
     C                     MOVELSTTHI2    SKTHI2           *LOT NUMBER 2
     C                     MOVELSTTHMK    SKTHMK           *PURPOSE
     C                     MOVELSTDVKB    SKDVKB           *DIVISION
     C                     MOVELSTDPNM    SKDPNM           *DIVISION PERSON
     C                     MOVELSTVIKO    SKVIKO           *DESCRIPTION
     C                     MOVELSTTKNM    SKTKNM           *CUSTOMER NAME
     C                     Z-ADDSTNOHZ    SKNOHZ           *DELIVERY DATE
     C                     Z-ADDSTTHSU    SKTHSU           *DELIVERY QTY
     C                     MOVELSTSHN1    SKSHN1           *INHOUSE PART N
     C                     MOVELSTSHN2    SKSHN2           *INHOUSE PART N
     C                     MOVELSTSHN3    SKSHN3           *INHOUSE PART N
     C                     MOVELSTSMEI    SKSMEI           *PART NAME
     C                     MOVELSTMHN1    SKMHN1           *CUSTOMER PART
     C                     MOVELSTMHN2    SKMHN2           *CUSTOMER PART
     C                     MOVELSTMHN3    SKMHN3           *CUSTOMER PART
     C                     MOVELSTMHN4    SKMHN4           *CUSTOMER PART
     C                     MOVELSTBHN1    SKBHN1           *BLANK PART NUM
     C                     MOVELSTBHN2    SKBHN2           *BLANK PART NUM
     C                     MOVELSTBHN3    SKBHN3           *BLANK PART NUM
     C                     Z-ADDSTKUBI    SKKUBI           *NOMINAL LENGTH
     C                     Z-ADDSTSOZI    SKSOZI           *MATERIAL WEIGH
     C                     MOVELSTSOZT    SKSOZT           *MATERIAL WEIGH
     C                     Z-ADDSTKASI    SKKASI           *FINISHED WEIGH
     C                     MOVELSTKASK    SKKASK           *FINISHED WEIGH
     C                     MOVELSTZANM    SKZANM           *MATERIAL
     C                     MOVELSTZAIR    SKZAIR           *MATERIALS COLO
     C                     Z-ADDSTKAZI    SKKAZI           *WIRE DIAMETER
     C                     MOVELSTZBN1    SKZBN1           *WIRE LOCATION
     C                     MOVELSTZBN2    SKZBN2           *WIRE LOCATION
     C                     MOVELSTZBN3    SKZBN3           *WIRE LOCATION
     C                     MOVELSTZBN4    SKZBN4           *WIRE LOCATION
     C                     MOVELSTMEK1    SKMEK1           *SRFACE TREATME
     C                     MOVELSTMEK2    SKMEK2           *SRFACE TREATME
     C                     MOVELSTMEK3    SKMEK3           *SRFACE TREATME
     C                     Z-ADDSTMKSU    SKMKSU           *COEFFICIENT
     C                     MOVELSTMMEI    SKMMEI           *SRFACE TREATME
     C                     Z-ADDSTBLSU    SKBLSU           *BARREL
     C                     MOVELSTSETR    SKSETR           *SECOND SRFACE
     C                     MOVELSTSECD    SKSECD           *2ND SRFACE TR. CD.
     C                     Z-ADDSTTUSZ    SKTUSZ           *NOMINAL SIZE
     C                     Z-ADDSTKIKI    SKKIKI           *MATERIAL PROPE
     C                     Z-ADDSTOQTP    SKOQTP           *OQ TEMP
     C                     Z-ADDSTKPTM    SKKPTM           *KEEP TIME
     C                     Z-ADDSTTMTP    SKTMTP           *TEMPERING TEMP
     C                     Z-ADDSTCO2     SKCO2            *CO2(%)
     C                     Z-ADDSTOQLT    SKOQLT           *OQ LOT
     C                     Z-ADDSTLATP    SKLATP           *LAN/AOQ TEMP
     C                     Z-ADDSTLATM    SKLATM           *LAN/AOQ KEEP T
     C                     Z-ADDSTBSK1    SKBSK1           *BASCKET 1
     C                     Z-ADDSTBSK2    SKBSK2           *BASCKET 2
     C                     Z-ADDSTBSK3    SKBSK3           *BASCKET 3
     C                     Z-ADDSTBSK4    SKBSK4           *BASCKET 4
     C                     Z-ADDSTSSYS    SKSSYS           *CONTAINING QUA
     C                     MOVELSTSSYT    SKSSYT           *TYPE
     C                     Z-ADDSTSISU    SKSISU           *PRODUCTION QTY
     C                     Z-ADDSTHKSU    SKHKSU           *BOXES
     C                     Z-ADDSTHKJU    SKHKJU           *WEIGHT PER BOX
     C                     MOVELSTKH11    SKKH11           *COMPONENT PART
     C                     MOVELSTKH12    SKKH12           *COMPONENT PART
     C                     MOVELSTKH13    SKKH13           *COMPONENT PART
     C                     MOVELSTKB11    SKKB11           *COMPONENT LOCA
     C                     MOVELSTKB12    SKKB12           *COMPONENT LOCA
     C                     MOVELSTKB13    SKKB13           *COMPONENT LOCA
     C                     MOVELSTKB14    SKKB14           *COMPONENT LOCA
     C                     Z-ADDSTSKS1    SKSKS1           *COMPONENT PART
     C                     MOVELSTKOT1    SKKOT1           *ASSEMBLY CODE
     C                     MOVELSTKH21    SKKH21           *COMPONENT PART
     C                     MOVELSTKH22    SKKH22           *COMPONENT PART
     C                     MOVELSTKH23    SKKH23           *COMPONENT PART
     C                     MOVELSTKB21    SKKB21           *COMPONENT LOCA
     C                     MOVELSTKB22    SKKB22           *COMPONENT LOCA
     C                     MOVELSTKB23    SKKB23           *COMPONENT LOCA
     C                     MOVELSTKB24    SKKB24           *COMPONENT LOCA
     C                     Z-ADDSTSKS2    SKSKS2           *COMPONENT PART
     C                     MOVELSTKOT2    SKKOT2           *ASSEMBLY CODE
     C                     MOVELSTKH31    SKKH31           *COMPONENT PART
     C                     MOVELSTKH32    SKKH32           *COMPONENT PART
     C                     MOVELSTKH33    SKKH33           *COMPONENT PART
     C                     MOVELSTKB31    SKKB31           *COMPONENT LOCA
     C                     MOVELSTKB32    SKKB32           *COMPONENT LOCA
     C                     MOVELSTKB33    SKKB33           *COMPONENT LOCA
     C                     MOVELSTKB34    SKKB34           *COMPONENT LOCA
     C                     Z-ADDSTSKS3    SKSKS3           *COMPONENT PART
     C                     MOVELSTKOT3    SKKOT3           *ASSEMBLY CODE
     C                     MOVELSTKH41    SKKH41           *COMPONENT PART
     C                     MOVELSTKH42    SKKH42           *COMPONENT PART
     C                     MOVELSTKH43    SKKH43           *COMPONENT PART
     C                     MOVELSTKB41    SKKB41           *COMPONENT LOCA
     C                     MOVELSTKB42    SKKB42           *COMPONENT LOCA
     C                     MOVELSTKB43    SKKB43           *COMPONENT LOCA
     C                     MOVELSTKB44    SKKB44           *COMPONENT LOCA
     C                     Z-ADDSTSKS4    SKSKS4           *COMPONENT PART
     C                     MOVELSTKOT4    SKKOT4           *ASSEMBLY CODE
     C                     Z-ADDSTWAHZ    SKWAHZ           *WASHER DELIVER
     C                     Z-ADDSTZRHZ    SKZRHZ           *MATELIAL DELIV
     C                     Z-ADDSTKTHZ    SKKTHZ           *TOOL DELIVERY
     C                     MOVELSTBAN1    SKBAN1           *LOCATION CODE
     C                     MOVELSTBAN2    SKBAN2           *LOCATION CODE
     C                     MOVELSTBAN3    SKBAN3           *LOCATION CODE
     C                     MOVELSTBAN4    SKBAN4           *LOCATION CODE
     C                     Z-ADDSTKTNO    SKKTNO           *PROCESS NO.
     C                     MOVELSTKTEI    SKKTEI           *PROCESS CODE
     C                     Z-ADDSTKBMN    SKKBMN           *FACTORY
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    SKKBNA           *FACTORY NAME
     C                     MOVELSTINSP    SKINSP           *INSP
     C                     MOVELSTHNL1    SKHNL1           *HN LOC1
     C                     MOVELSTHNL2    SKHNL2           *HN LOC2
     C                     MOVELSTHNL3    SKHNL3           *HN LOC3
     C                     MOVELSTHNL4    SKHNL4           *HN LOC4
      *細目コード管理マスタ(FGBPL01)
     C                     Z-ADDSKKBMN    B2CODE           *細目コード
     C           B2KEY     CHAINFGBPL011             81
     C           *IN81     IFEQ '0'                        ¬IF_01
     C           B2SKJY    IFEQ 'D'                        ~¬IF_02
     C           B2SKHZ    ANDLES@YYMD
      *(処理無し)
     C                     ELSE                            -+ELSE_02
     C                     MOVELB2SMEI    SKKBNA           *加工工場名称
     C                     END                             _｢IF_02
     C                     END                             ｢IF_01
      *
     C                     MOVELSTBCCD    SKBCCD           *BOX COLOR
     C                     MOVELSTBCNM    SKBCNM           *BOX COLOR NAME
     C                     MOVELSTMSNO    SKMSNO           *MACHINE NO.
     C                     Z-ADDSTKNHZ    SKKNHZ           *PROCESS DATE
     C                     MOVELSTKVIK    SKKVIK           *PROCESS DESCRI
      *<バーコード項目>
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    SKMKBA           *SRFACE TREATMENT
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    SKCGBA           *CHKCK GATE
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    SKBFLG           *OQ LOQ FLG
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    SKOQBA           *OQ
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    SKLOQB           *LOQ
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    SKSTBA           *SECOND SRFACE
      *
     C                     MOVELSTBFLG    SKBFLG           *OQFLG
      * SURFACE TREATMENT BARCODE
     C                     MOVEL'A'       SKMKB1           *SRFACE TREATMENT
     C                     MOVELSKTHI1    SKMKB2           *SRFACE TREATMENT
     C                     MOVE SKTHI2    SKMKB2           *SRFACE TREATMENT
     C                     MOVEL'01'      SKMKB3           *SRFACE TREATMENT
     C                     MOVEL'050C'    SKMKB4           *SRFACE TREATMENT
     C*
     C                     MOVELSKMKB     PMAREA100
     C                     MOVEL'014'     PMBYTE  3
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    PMCHK   1
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    PMRTCD  1
     C                     CALL 'ALBRCC'
     C                     PARM           PMAREA
     C                     PARM           PMBYTE
     C                     PARM           PMCHK
     C                     PARM           PMRTCD
     C                     MOVELPMCHK     SKMKCD           *SRFACE TREATMENT
      *
      *
     C*                    MOVELSKTHI1    SKMKB2           *SRFACE TREATMENT
     C*                    MOVELSKTHI2    SKMKB3           *SRFACE TREATMENT
      *チェックゲートバーコード
     C                     MOVELSKTHI1    SKCGB1           *CHKCK GATE
     C                     MOVELSKTHI2    SKCGB2           *CHKCK GATE
      *OQ LOQ BARCODE
     C                     SELEC
     C           STBFLG    WHEQ '1'                        ¬IF_01
     C                     MOVE SKTMTP    SKOQB1           *OQ
     C                     MOVE SKCO2     SKOQB2           *OQ
     C                     MOVE SKTHI1    SKOQB3           *OQ
     C*
     C                     MOVELSKOQB     PMAREA100
     C                     MOVEL'010'     PMBYTE  3
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    PMCHK   1
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    PMRTCD  1
     C                     CALL 'ALBRCC'
     C                     PARM           PMAREA
     C                     PARM           PMBYTE
     C                     PARM           PMCHK
     C                     PARM           PMRTCD
     C                     MOVE PMCHK     SKOQCD           *OQ
      *
      *LOQ BARCODE
     C           STBFLG    WHEQ '2'                         WH
     C                     MOVE SKTMTP    SKLOQ1           *OQ焼き入れ時間
     C           STZANM    IFEQ 'SCM35-B'
     C                     MOVE '050'     SKLOQ2
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE '045'     SKLOQ2
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     MOVELSKLOQ     PMAREA100
     C                     MOVEL'006'     PMBYTE  3
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    PMCHK   1
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    PMRTCD  1
     C                     CALL 'ALBRCC'
     C                     PARM           PMAREA
     C                     PARM           PMBYTE
     C                     PARM           PMCHK
     C                     PARM           PMRTCD
     C                     MOVELPMCHK     SKLOQC
     C*
     C                     ENDSL                           _｢IF_02
      *
      *<前回手配発行日>
     C                     Z-ADDSTLPHZ    SKLPHZ           *LAST PRINT DATE
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      *          #MOV20   項目移送処理
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #MOV20    BEGSR
      *試作手配データファイル(MRHPL53)
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    STGSJY           * DELETE CODE D
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     STGSHZ           * DELETE DATE
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    STGSNM           * DELETE PERSON
     C                     Z-ADDS@YYMD    STGKHZ           * UPDATE DATE
     C                     Z-ADDS@HMS     STGKTM           * UPDATE TIME
     C                     MOVELS@PGID    STGKPG           * UPDATE PROGRAM
     C                     MOVELS@USID    STGKNM           * UPDATE PERSON
      *
     C                     Z-ADDS@YYMD    STHKHZ           * KANBAN PRINT DATE
     C                     Z-ADDS@HMS     STHKTM           * KANBAN PRINT TIME
     C                     Z-ADDS@YYMD    STLPHZ           * LAST PRINT DATE
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------------------
